The paper deals with image processing, specifically image deconvolution and decomposition, which falls under the computer vision (cs.CV) sub-category. The use of partial differential equations and multiscale sampling theory suggests that the paper may also be relevant to information theory (cs.IT), multimedia (cs.MM), numerical analysis (cs.NA), and signal processing (cs.SI) sub-categories.
